nfiguration {\n\n        @Bean\n        RecordingTransactionManager transactionManager() {\n            return new RecordingTransactionManager();\n        }\n\n\n[207 more lines in file. Use offset=261 to continue.]"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1779186612698}}
